<h3>
	Location
</h3>
<p>
	The Remembranmce Gallery is located under the Grandstand at <a href="https://thefair.com">the Washington State Fair</a>. The closest entrances are the Gold Gate and the Red Gate.
</p>

<address>
	Washington State Fair<br/>
	110 9th Ave SW<br/>
	Puyallup, WA 98371
</address>

